{"id":699991,"date":[{"year":1985,"month":5,"day":14}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会(游记专辑)","column":"","genre":"","count":"142","ytitle":"","mtitle":"游古猗园","ftitle":"","authors":["童苏群"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"童苏群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尚书营建古猗园，平地难能别有天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九曲桥头商改革，戏鹅池畔乐余年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沪客闲休每欲游，猗园权作小扬州；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时逢两代人交接，四化欢开不系舟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三省曾惊拱手丢，自家骨肉竟成仇；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万亭缺角当年望，谁不凭轩涕泗流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缺角亭高寄远情，羁台少帅苦凄清；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白山黑水今多秀，蒋氏何亏统一明。"}]}